title: Casanova Is Living In My House
itunes:title: Casanova Is Living In My House
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I am a 55 year old mother, still raising a 24 year old man and he’s still living in my house. All of my family calls him Casanova because he’s very handsome with a head full of black curls. He’s never been full of himself, but he’s well aware of how good he looks. He’s never been in a relationship and when he was in high school, girls used to call my house so much I had to restrict calls sometimes..................
